	* Remove trailing whitespace and CRs/"\r"s.

	* Fix the rpm .spec to use the .tar.xz archive.

Version 0.16.0 - shlomif - 2016-03-23

	* Fix the rpm .spec generation and modernised/updated the rpm .spec.

